  "instructions": [
    "In a large mixing bowl, combine flour and salt; whisk to combine.",
    "Gradually add warm water to dry ingredients; mix until a dough forms.",
    "Knead dough for 5-7 minutes until smooth and elastic.",
    "Place dough in a greased bowl; let it rise in a warm place for an hour.",
    "Preheat a steamer; prepare a steamer basket with parchment paper.",
    "Punch down dough; divide into small balls.",
    "Roll each ball into a thin circle.",
    "Place a tablespoon of stuffing in the center of each circle.",
    "Fold dough over filling, forming a half-moon shape.",
    "Steam baos for 15-20 minutes until cooked through.",
    "Serve warm with a dollop of sour cream and a sprinkle of black pepper."
